entries.stormtrooper_neutral_see_death_1: Looks like it's over for now.
entries.stormtrooper_neutral_see_attack_1: Fighting going on.  I'm waiting for orders...
entries.stormtrooper_neutral_greeting_1: Are you authorized to be here?
entries.stormtrooper_like_see_attack_1: Stand aside, I'll deal with this!
entries.stormtrooper_dislike_farewell_1: You're not authorized to be here.
entries.hutt_overhear_name_1: I didn't do it, whatever you're talking about.

entries.hutt_neutral_see_death_1: I wonder if I can use this to my advantage somehow.

entries.hutt_dislike_see_death: Too bad you can't bring him back and kill him again.
entries.hutt_like_see_attack_1: Keep your head down, I'll try to help!

entries.hutt_neutral_greeting_1: What can you do for me?

entries.hutt_dislike_greeting_1: I don't have time for your petty troubles.
entries.rebel_offer_mission_1: Can you do the alliance a small favor?

entries.rebel_mission_accepted_1: The alliance thanks you for your help.
entries.rebel_like_see_death_1: Oh, no!  That was my friend!
entries.rebel_dislike_see_death_1: They got what was coming to them.
entries.rebel_like_farewell_1: May the force be with you.
entries.rebel_like_greeting_1: Hey, how are you?  Can I help you with anything?
entries.rebel_dislike_greeting_1: Oh, it's you.  What is it now?
entries.imperial_offer_mission_1: Are you ready to do some work for the glory of the empire?
entries.imperial_mission_declined_1: Well, some people just don't have what it takes.
entries.imperial_mission_accepted_1: Very good.  Now get to work.
entries.imperial_victory_1: Yes!  That was for the Emperor's glory!
entries.imperial_dislike_see_death_1: That's one less problem to worry about.

entries.imperial_neutral_see_attack_1: Be more careful, I could have been hurt.
entries.imperial_like_greeting_1: Good day!  What can I do for you?
entries.imperial_neutral_greeting_1: What can I do for you?
entries.neutral_mission_declined_1: That's too bad.  I need to find someone to help me.
entries.neutral_mission_accepted_1: Fantastic.  I'm sure you'll get it done.
entries.neutral_offer_mission_1: Can you do me a small favor?
entries.neutral_dislike_see_death_1: I never liked that person much anyway.
entries.neutral_like_see_death_1: Oh no!  My friend is dead!
entries.neutral_like_see_attack_1: Hey!  Stop that!  That's my friend!
entries.neutral_overhear_name_1: Excuse me?  Did you mean me?
entries.neutral_like_farewell_1: See you later!  Don't be a stranger.
entries.neutral_like_greeting_1: Hi there!  How are things going?
entries.neutral_neutral_greeting_1: Yes?  What can I do for you?
entries.neutral_dislike_greeting_1: Oh, it's you again.  What do you need now?
